    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0893c23"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>金陵莊嚴寺<persName key="A008826">慧涉</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0893c24"/><persName key="A008826">釋慧涉</persName>，俗姓謝氏，<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName>人也。即東晉太傅<persName key="A002691">安</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0893c25"/>之後。是知傑氣英靈，間代而出。律梁拔俗，異<lb
ed="T" n="0893c26"/>世豈無？<persName key="A008826">涉</persName>為人清素，戒節孤峻，好寂為樂，<lb
ed="T" n="0893c27"/>不棲名聞。以<date key="j20011912002330" notAfter-iso="0770" notBefore-iso="0766">大曆之初</date>，於金陵<placeName key="PL000000008702">莊嚴寺</placeName>遇<lb
ed="T" n="0893c28"/>牛頭山<persName key="A010048">忠禪師</persName>，一言知歸，遂命入室，授其<lb
ed="T" n="0893c29"/>法要。服膺道化，待之彌載，不憚其勞。洎<pb ed="T" n="0894a" xml:id="T50.2061.0894a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0894a01"/><persName key="A010048">忠</persName>捐世，踵武茲嶺，無遊人境。一衣方丈，操<lb
ed="T" n="0894a02"/>節彌高。自是以來，問道者眾，四維方域，無<lb
ed="T" n="0894a03"/>不霑洽，五十年中，翕然歸德。以<date key="j20213202021703" notAfter-iso="0823-02-18" notBefore-iso="0822-01-31">長慶二年</date><lb
ed="T" n="0894a04"/>終於<placeName key="PL000000008702">山院</placeName>，春秋八十有二。門弟子<persName key="A013918">惟晏</persName>等奉<lb
ed="T" n="0894a05"/>全師禮，建塔於<placeName key="PL000000008702">寺</placeName>之西北，勒銘紀德。若考<lb
ed="T" n="0894a06"/><persName key="A008826">師</persName>之藝文，則草堂<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬嶽</placeName>，各美於當代矣。</p>
